data.description: Welcome to this stunning, brand new 2100+ square-foot modern home build! This exceptional property boasts a contemporary design with all the bells and whistles you could ever dream of. Step outside and be greeted by a luxurious pebble tech pool, perfect for those hot summer days and relaxing evenings. Dive in and let the worries of the day melt away in this oasis of serenity. As you explore further, you'll be delighted to discover a huge bar and entertainment space located right in the garage. This space is ideal for hosting unforgettable gatherings, complete with air-conditioning to ensure your guests' comfort, no matter the weather. Inside the house, the kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, making it a dream come true for any aspiring chef. From sleek, stainless steel finishes to state-of-the-art functionality, this kitchen is designed to inspire culinary creativity. But that s not all! This home also features a convenient dog wash area, perfect for pampering your four-legged friends after a long day of play. For car enthusiasts or those in need of ample storage space, the property offers a 4-car garage, providing plenty of room for vehicles, toys, and any other belongings you may have. This modern home build truly combines luxury, style, and functionality in every aspect. Don't miss the opportunity to live in this exceptional property that exudes charm and modern elegance. Come and see it for yourself as it won't be available for long!
